Abengoa to Present Offer to Delist Befesa Environmental Unit Within Month

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-04-26T07:08:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/abengoa-to-present-offer-to-delist-befesa-environmental-unit-within-month.html
Abengoa SA (ABG)  will present its offer
to delist its unit  Befesa Medio Ambiente SA (BMA)  at 26 euros a share
within a month, Befesa said in a regulatory filing today. The
offer was first announced on March 17.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  